            <foreign>makkaḷ</foreign>
          </supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied>  <gap reason="ellipsis"/>, seized cattle <gap reason="ellipsis"/> when being <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>iruntu</foreign>
          </supplied> <gap reason="ellipsis"/> in Mēṟkoṉṟaināṭu, on the northern bank of the Peṇṇai <supplied reason="subaudible">river</supplied>.
